USAGE

get headers for libvorbis-dev and libpng-dev

cpan Alien::SDL
  choose to compile

Click Download Source http://github.com/kthakore/SDL_perl/tree/redesign
   Extract it 
   perl Build.PL; perl Build; perl Build install


This game has the following dependencies, all of which 
can be installed from CPAN:

  * JSON::Any
  * Mouse   
  * Math::Trig


perl spinner.pl


